12::[Battles]::
2Battles happen automatically every 5 minutes after a previous battle has ended.  These battles are the primary source of earning Red Orbs and Black Orbs.
2There are two types of battles: Boss and Normal battles.  In boss battles players will face off against 1 powerful foe, while normal battles may be against multiple foes.
